dct_description_sm: Prepared by the U.S. Geological Survey for publication by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Variant title: Indiana 1:50,000. Standard map series designation: DMA series V751 Sheet 3862 III. Edition 1--DMA. Transverse Mercator projection. DMA series , V751. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Shows roads, railroads, boundaries, mines, and man made and natural features. Marginal index maps: Elevation guide -- Adjoining sheets -- Boundaries. Contour interval 10 feet. "Printed by GMAHTC 1-83." "DMA stock no. V751X38623."
Imprint: Washington, D.C. : Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center, [1983]; Imprint: Distributor: Reston, Virgina : Geological Survey, [1983]
Dimensions: 56 x 45 cm or smaller; Scale: 1:50,000
dct_publisher_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Topographic Center
